  - id: ossa_tarsi
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Ossa Tarsi
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "alt ekstremite; ayak; ayak bile\u011Fi; k\u0131sa; tarsal"
    body: "Ayak bile\u011Finde yer alan k\u0131sa kemik grubudur."
    steps: "[\"Ayak bile\u011Finde iki s\u0131ra halinde dizilmi\u015F 7 k\u0131sa
      kemik bulunur.\", \"Bald\u0131r kemikleri ile ayak tarak kemikleri aras\u0131nda
      yer al\u0131r.\", \"A\u015F\u0131k kemi\u011Fi (os talus), tibia ve fibula
      ile ayak bile\u011Fi eklemini olu\u015Fturur.\", \"Ayak bile\u011Findeki en
      b\xFCy\xFCk kemik topuk kemi\u011Fidir (os calcaneus).\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.65"
  - id: ossa_metatarsi
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: bone
    title: Ossa Metatarsi
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: alt ekstremite; ayak; tarak; uzun; metatarsal
    body: "Ayak taban\u0131 ve ayak s\u0131rt\u0131n\u0131n iskeletini olu\u015Fturan
      kemik grubudur."
    steps: "[\"5 uzun kemikten olu\u015Fur.\", \"Ayak bile\u011Fi kemikleri ile ayak
      parmak kemikleri aras\u0131nda yer al\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.65"
  - id: ossa_digitorum_pedis
    valence: learn
