  - id: m_gluteus_maximus
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: M. Gluteus Maximus
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "kas; kal\xE7a; b\xFCy\xFCk kal\xE7a; kal\u0131n; ekstans\xF6r; ekstansiyon;
      d\u0131\u015F rotasyon"
    body: "V\xFCcudun en kal\u0131n kas\u0131d\u0131r. \u0130liumun d\u0131\u015F
      y\xFCz\xFC ve sakrumdan ba\u015Flay\u0131p femurda sonlan\u0131r. \u0130liopsoas
      kas\u0131n\u0131n antagonistidir."
    steps: "[\"Uylu\u011Fun en g\xFC\xE7l\xFC ekstans\xF6r kas\u0131d\u0131r.\" ,
      \"Uylu\u011Fa ekstansiyon ve d\u0131\u015Fa rotasyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.81"
  - id: m_gluteus_medius
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: M. Gluteus Medius
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "kas; kal\xE7a; orta kal\xE7a; abd\xFCkt\xF6r"
    body: "B\xFCy\xFCk kal\xE7a kas\u0131n\u0131n alt\u0131nda yar al\u0131r. Le\u011Fen
      kemi\u011Finden ba\u015Flay\u0131p femurda sonlan\u0131r."
