  - id: m_sartorius
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: M. Sartorius
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "kas; uyluk; terzi; uzun; fleksiyon; abd\xFCksiyon; i\xE7 rotasyon"
    body: "V\xFCcudun en uzun kas\u0131d\u0131r. Le\u011Fen kemi\u011Finden ba\u015Flay\u0131p
      \xF6n i\xE7 yan\u0131ndan ge\xE7erek tibia kemi\u011Finin \xFCst ucunda sonlan\u0131r."
    steps: "[\"Uylu\u011Fa fleksiyon ve abd\xFCksiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\" , \"Diz
      yar\u0131m fleksiyondayken bald\u0131ra i\xE7 rotasyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
    source: "Ders kitab\u0131 s.82"
  - id: m_quadriceps_femoris
