  - id: hamstring
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: Hamstring Grubu Kaslar
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: kas; uyluk; arka adele; ekstansiyon; fleksiyon
    body: "Arka adele de denir. \xDC\xE7 kastan (m. biceps femoris"
    steps: ' m. semitendinosus'
    source: " m. semimembranosus) olu\u015Fur. Bu kaslar oturak kemi\u011Finden ba\u015Flay\u0131p
      tibia ve fibula kemi\u011Finde sonlan\u0131r. Sporcular\u0131n en \xE7ok sakatland\u0131klar\u0131
      kaslar\u0131n ba\u015F\u0131nda gelir."
  - id: m_tibialis_anterior
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: M. Tibialis Anterior
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "kas; bald\u0131r; \xF6n tibia; dorsifleksiyon; ekstansiyon; inversiyon"
    body: "Tibia kemi\u011Finin \xF6n"
    steps: " d\u0131\u015F ve yan taraf\u0131nda bulunur. Tibia kemi\u011Finin \xFCst
      ucundan ba\u015Flay\u0131p birinci ayak tarak kemi\u011Finde sonlan\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Aya\u011Fa dorsifleksiyon (ekstansiyon) ve inversiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: m_tibialis_posterior
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: M. Tibialis Posterior
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "kas; bald\u0131r; arka tibia; plantar fleksiyon; inversiyon"
    body: "Tibia ve fibula kemi\u011Finin arkas\u0131nda bulunur. Buradan ba\u015Flay\u0131p
      2"
    steps: " 3 ve 4\u2019\xFCnc\xFC ayak tarak kemi\u011Finde sonlan\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Aya\u011Fa plantar fleksiyon ve inversiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
  - id: m_triceps_surae
    valence: learn
    doc_type: entry
    content_type: muscle
    title: M. Triceps Surae
    topic: Movement System
    region: Lower_Extremity
    tags: "kas; bald\u0131r; \xFC\xE7 ba\u015Fl\u0131; a\u015Fil tendonu; plantar
      fleksiyon"
    body: "Bald\u0131r\u0131n arkas\u0131ndaki kabar\u0131kl\u0131\u011F\u0131 yapan
      kast\u0131r. Bu kas"
    steps: " m. gastrocnemius ve m. soleus kas\u0131n\u0131n birle\u015Fmesinden
      olu\u015Fur. \u0130ki kas tibian\u0131n \xFCst ucundan ba\u015Flay\u0131p a\u015Fil
      tendonunu olu\u015Fturduktan sonra topuk kemi\u011Finde sonlan\u0131r."
    source: "[\"Aya\u011Fa plantar fleksiyon yapt\u0131r\u0131r.\"]"
